<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Uniqlo X Sailor Moon</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Altogether, the fusion&nbsp;of manga&nbsp;culture and popular fashion amalgamates&nbsp;vivid visuals and unparalleled artistry in a way that reminiscent of the playful nature of anime and the importance of clothing design. Many designers have recognized the fine line between the two art forms and have&nbsp;consequently created many memorable&nbsp;<a href="https://www.lofficielusa.com/fashion/young-kate-moss-90s-style-runway" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">runway moments</a>.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>1&nbsp;/&nbsp;7</p>
